					<p>3. <hi rend="italic">Bonosi laudea.</hi> — Bonosus, ut scribitis, quasi <lb/> lilius
							<hi rend="italic">(d)</hi> 19 <foreign xml:lang="grc">ίχθύος</foreign>, id cst,
